QuestData.Title: Flying Colors
QuestData.Description: The Rumpus was your final test. You have mastered the disciplines taught at this monastery.$b$bJust as your training began with a banquet, so shall it end. High Elder Cloudfall should be waiting at the banquet grounds. I'll be right behind you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to High Elder Cloudfall at the Banquet Grounds in the Jade Forest.
